  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/b541f306e9dabf7a8f9abee015d41402.avif?t=1760099580\" width=460 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A new sensation!? City-building × Roguelike game *Super Tax City*. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose and place your favorite facilities from randomly drawn options!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The combinations are endless! Create a profitable city that's uniquely yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Rules</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose a facility from three options and place it on the map!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/d02885f65436c160a365fd2999d0a3ce.poster.avif?t=1760099580\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/d02885f65436c160a365fd2999d0a3ce.webm?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/d02885f65436c160a365fd2999d0a3ce.mp4?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When randomly moving residents enter a facility, they perform tasks and earn rewards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/b951bcac73b4744e8a660ff5faad17de.poster.avif?t=1760099580\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/b951bcac73b4744e8a660ff5faad17de.webm?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/b951bcac73b4744e8a660ff5faad17de.mp4?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When the time limit expires, it's tax time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay your taxes with the money you've earned!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/2c12ff7f56641005f5812cf66c40c6b4.poster.avif?t=1760099580\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/2c12ff7f56641005f5812cf66c40c6b4.webm?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/2c12ff7f56641005f5812cf66c40c6b4.mp4?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the Facilities</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100 types of unique facilities with distinctive effects are featured!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/625a3b5c3ca86292ff4fb0d0e7247fcc.poster.avif?t=1760099580\" width=600 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/625a3b5c3ca86292ff4fb0d0e7247fcc.webm?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/625a3b5c3ca86292ff4fb0d0e7247fcc.mp4?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About the items</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your city even further with over 100 different items!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/16d3d1cccbfc2817942b3fd637cd2d93.poster.avif?t=1760099580\" width=600 height=192 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/16d3d1cccbfc2817942b3fd637cd2d93.webm?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/16d3d1cccbfc2817942b3fd637cd2d93.mp4?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The combinations are endless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create a profitable city that's uniquely yours!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/66a240a6a161d3ab6361cdd6b3429d19.poster.avif?t=1760099580\" width=598 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/66a240a6a161d3ab6361cdd6b3429d19.webm?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2881800/extras/66a240a6a161d3ab6361cdd6b3429d19.mp4?t=1760099580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Streaming Guidelines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1) You are free to stream and upload gameplay videos without prior notice, regardless of whether you are an individual or corporation, and regardless of whether your activities are for profit or not.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2) If possible, please include the URL of the Steam page in the description.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3) We take no responsibility for any damages that may occur as a result of streaming this game. Additionally, the content of these guidelines may be changed without prior notice.</p>",
